[{"slug":"about","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"70\" class=\"elementor elementor-70\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c51494a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c51494a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c8ebbae elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c8ebbae\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">About Us<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15d53ec e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"15d53ec\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f5c1618 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f5c1618\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-be21062 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"be21062\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Welcome to RatingE<\/h6>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-893fc97 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"893fc97\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Welcome to RatingE, where we empower businesses to build trust, enhance visibility, and grow through the power of authentic customer reviews.<\/p><p>Our mission is to simplify and automate the review collection process, making it effortless for businesses of all sizes to attract more customers and improve their online reputation.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9226b4e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"9226b4e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ceb290a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ceb290a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/E.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-134\" alt=\"RateingE icon\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/E.png 500w, https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/E-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/E-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-755e7ac e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"755e7ac\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2273595 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2273595\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1466807 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1466807\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>RatingE was founded with a simple yet powerful vision: to help businesses thrive in an increasingly competitive digital landscape. We understand that in today&#8217;s world, a strong online presence is essential for success.<\/p><p>That&#8217;s why we&#8217;ve developed an AI-powered platform that streamlines the review process, allowing you to focus on what you do best\u2014running your business.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d2bc299 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"d2bc299\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-31ad01a animation-wobble elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"31ad01a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"468\" height=\"765\" src=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Who-we-are.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-614\" alt=\"Who we are\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Who-we-are.png 468w, https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Who-we-are-184x300.png 184w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 468px) 100vw, 468px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-245051b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"245051b\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9dcf86a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"9dcf86a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8313409 animation-wobble elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8313409\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"468\" height=\"765\" src=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/main.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-661\" alt=\"RatingE- Comprehensive solution to online Reputation management\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/main.webp 468w, https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/main-184x300.webp 184w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 468px) 100vw, 468px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-09580f6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"09580f6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-435438f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"435438f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>At RatingE, we offer a comprehensive suite of tools designed to automate and enhance your review management efforts.<\/p><p>From automated email sequences and SMS requests to customizable QR codes and video testimonials, our platform is equipped with everything you need to collect, manage, and display positive reviews across multiple channels.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-64da40c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"64da40c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-352253b e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"352253b\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e435be4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e435be4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>We are committed to delivering top-notch service and innovative solutions that meet the unique needs of each business we serve.<\/p><p>Our team of experts works tirelessly to ensure that our platform is always up-to-date with the latest technology and best practices, providing you with a seamless experience that drives results.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-163e628 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"163e628\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-926aeb4 animation-wobble elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"926aeb4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"468\" height=\"765\" src=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Hero2.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-32\" alt=\"Hero\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Hero2.png 468w, https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Hero2-184x300.png 184w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 468px) 100vw, 468px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-22dc163 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"22dc163\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f9eeb32 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f9eeb32\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2694108 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2694108\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>With RatingE, you gain more than just a review management tool\u2014you gain a partner dedicated to your success. We take care of the technical details, from customization to legal paperwork, so you can concentrate on growing your business.<\/p><p>Plus, our platform is designed to be user-friendly, ensuring that you can get up and running with minimal effort.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a7ff8e3 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a7ff8e3\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d178138 animation-wobble elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"d178138\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"468\" height=\"765\" src=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Hero4.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-47\" alt=\"Review\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Hero4.png 468w, https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Hero4-184x300.png 184w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 468px) 100vw, 468px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-933f8ae e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"933f8ae\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7f7c0ba e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7f7c0ba\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-16f6e44 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"16f6e44\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Join the growing community of businesses that trust RatingE to boost their online reputation and attract more customers. Whether you&#8217;re a small business owner or a large enterprise, we&#8217;re here to help you succeed in today&#8217;s digital world.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-34f866d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"34f866d\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fd5a21b animation-wobble elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"fd5a21b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"468\" height=\"765\" src=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Hero4-1.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-607\" alt=\"Join Us\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Hero4-1.png 468w, https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Hero4-1-184x300.png 184w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 468px) 100vw, 468px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>About Us Welcome to RatingE Transform Your Business with Effortless Review Management Welcome to RatingE, where we empower businesses to build trust, enhance visibility, and grow through the power of authentic customer reviews. Our mission is to simplify and automate the review collection process, making it effortless for businesses of all sizes to attract more [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false}}]